"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H11333238\">",
"      Is there a test for sickle cell anemia?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H11333253\">",
"      How is sickle cell anemia treated?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H11333268\">",
"      When should I call the doctor or nurse?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H11333283\">",
"      What else can people with sickle cell anemia do to stay healthy?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H11333298\">",
"      What if I have sickle cell anemia and want to get pregnant?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H11333313\">",
"      More on this topic",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"   </ul>",
